info.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 05 at 3:42AM PST until February 06 at 12:00PM PST by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 PM THIS EVENING TO NOON PST MONDAY... * WHAT...North winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 50 mph expected. * WHERE...Santa Ynez Mountains Western Range, Santa Ynez Mountains Eastern Range and Santa Barbara County Interior Mountains. * WHEN...From 9 PM this evening to noon PST Monday. * IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and make driving difficult, especially for high profile vehicles. Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
info.instruction: Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.
